{% macro conductReportDetails_v2(conductReportData) %}
    <div class='govuk-!-margin-left-8 govuk-!-margin-right-8'>
        <hr class='govuk-section-break govuk-section-break--m govuk-section-break--visible'>

        <div class='adjudication-pdf-section-prisoner govuk-!-width-full'>
            <div class='adjudication-pdf-section-prisoner__item'>
                <p class='govuk-!-margin-bottom-0 govuk-!-font-weight-bold'>Name</p>
                <p class='govuk-!-margin-bottom-0'
                   data-qa='notice-of-being-placed-on-report-prisoner-display-name'>
                    {{ conductReportData.prisonerDisplayName }}
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class='adjudication-pdf-section-prisoner__item'>
                <p class='govuk-!-margin-bottom-0 govuk-!-font-weight-bold'>Prison number</p>
                <p class='govuk-!-margin-bottom-0'
                   data-qa='notice-of-being-placed-on-report-prisoner-number'>
                    {{ conductReportData.prisonerNumber }}
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class='adjudication-pdf-section-prisoner__item'>
                <p class='govuk-!-margin-bottom-0 govuk-!-font-weight-bold'>Location</p>
                <p class='govuk-!-margin-bottom-0'
                   data-qa='notice-of-being-placed-on-report-prisoner-location-description'>
                    {{ conductReportData.prisonerLocationDescription }}
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class='adjudication-pdf-section-prisoner__item'>
                <p class='govuk-!-margin-bottom-0 govuk-!-font-weight-bold'>Key worker</p>
                <input type='text' class='adjudication-pdf-input adjudication-pdf-input-issuing-officer'>
            </div>
        </div>

        <hr class='govuk-section-break govuk-section-break--m govuk-section-break--visible'>

        <div>
            <p>This conduct report should be completed by an officer with good knowledge of the prisoner,</br>
               but <strong>not</strong> the officer who placed the prisoner on report.
            </p>

            <p>The report should be about the prisonerâ€™s behaviour, on the wing or other unit, during their</br>
               current sentence. Include any relevant dates and any comments on:
            </p>
            <ul class='govuk-list govuk-list--bullet'>
                <li class='govuk-!-margin-bottom-1'>open ACCT</li>
                <li class='govuk-!-margin-bottom-1'>CSIP</li>
                <li class='govuk-!-margin-bottom-1'>mental health referrals</li>
                <li class='govuk-!-margin-bottom-1'>debt</li>
                <li class='govuk-!-margin-bottom-1'>positive or negative incentive comments on Digital Prison Services (DPS)</li>
                <li class='govuk-!-margin-bottom-1'>case note</li>
                <li class='govuk-!-margin-bottom-1'>engagement in work or education (while in prison)</li>
                <li class='govuk-!-margin-bottom-1'>other relevant information, like drug support or other interventions</li>
            </ul>

            <p>The report must be based on facts and not opinion. It should not include details about criminal</br>
               history, adjudication history or employment.
            </p>

            <input type='text' class='adjudication-pdf-input adjudication-pdf-conduct-statement'>

            <div class='adjudication-pdf-section-signature-details'>
                <div class='adjudication-pdf-section-signature-details__item'>
                    <p class='govuk-!-margin-bottom-1 govuk-!-margin-top-3'>Signature of officer</p>
                    <input type='text' class='adjudication-pdf-input adjudication-pdf-input-text-box-half-width'>
                </div>
                <div class='adjudication-pdf-section-signature-details__item'>
                    <p class='govuk-!-margin-bottom-1 govuk-!-margin-top-3'>Name (BLOCK CAPITALS)</p>
                    <input type='text' class='adjudication-pdf-input adjudication-pdf-input-text-box-half-width'>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class='adjudication-pdf-section-signature-details'>
                <div class='adjudication-pdf-section-signature-details__item'>
                </div>
                <div class='adjudication-pdf-section-signature-details__item'>
                    <p class='govuk-!-margin-bottom-1 govuk-!-margin-top-1'>Date (DD/MM/YYYY)</p>
                    <input type='text' class='adjudication-pdf-input adjudication-pdf-input__square'><input type='text'  class='adjudication-pdf-input adjudication-pdf-input__square'><span><strong> / </strong></span><input type='text'  class='adjudication-pdf-input adjudication-pdf-input__square'><input type='text'  class='adjudication-pdf-input adjudication-pdf-input__square'><span><strong> / </strong></span><input type='text'  class='adjudication-pdf-input adjudication-pdf-input__square'><input type='text'  class='adjudication-pdf-input adjudication-pdf-input__square'><input type='text'  class='adjudication-pdf-input adjudication-pdf-input__square'><input type='text'  class='adjudication-pdf-input adjudication-pdf-input__square'>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

{% endmacro %}
